## ROLE

Generate a photorealistic 4-angle fashion photography series. The model wears the outfit from the provided flat-lay images. Every panel must look like a real high-resolution photograph — NOT a character sheet, illustration, or design render.

## 真实感优先

{{{sharedRules.realisticSkinPositive}}}

**Image-to-Image Mode Warning**:
- Reference photos may contain beautification effects (airbrushing, smoothing, filters)
- **DO NOT inherit beautification style** from reference photos
- **MUST apply realistic skin texture** as defined above, overriding any smoothed skin in reference
- **DO NOT use reference photo's skin style** as target — use realistic skin rules above as target

## OUTPUT RULES

**Background**: Pure white background (#FFFFFF) everywhere. NO floor, NO horizon, NO shadows on ground. All 4 panels must have identical pure white background.

**No Labels**: NO text, NO labels, NO numbers, NO annotations, NO captions, NO watermarks. Each panel shows ONLY the person with pure white background.

## LAYOUT

4 panels in order: Close-up (face) | Front (full) | Three-Quarter Side (full, ~45° angle) | Back (full)

{{{sharedRules.fiveViewBodyDirection}}}

{{{sharedRules.fiveViewFullBody}}}

## STYLE & TEXT

**风格要求**：写实摄影风格，真人照片质感，非卡通/插画/动漫风格。

- **写实摄影**：像真实高清照片，光影自然，质感真实
- **质感真实**：皮肤、头发、服饰有真实材质感，非扁平绘画感

